The paper discusses Pilot-Job systems, which are used in distributed scientific computing. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.Distributed (Distributed Computing), and cs.SC (Scientific Computing). The paper also discusses the implementation and architecture of Pilot-Job systems, which could place it in cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
